<span class="wims_code_words">jxgbox</span> et <span class="wims_code_words">jsxgraph_button</span>.
Par exemple,
</p>
<pre>
&lt;style>
.jxgbox {margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto}
.jsxgraph_button {text-align:center;}
